def_en: If someone breaks into a building, they get into it by force.
If someone breaks into something they suddenly start doing it. For example if someone breaks into a run they suddenly start running, and if they break into song they suddenly start singing.

def_cn: 成功打入，顺利进入（某行业，尤指很难取得成功的领域）
def_en: If you break into a profession or area of business, especially one that is difficult to succeed in, you manage to have some success in it.
